stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Intake: User submits task
    Intake --> RiskClassification
    RiskClassification --> LaneSelection: risk score 0-6+

    LaneSelection --> DIRECT: risk 0, 1 file
    LaneSelection --> FAST: risk 1-2, ≤3 files
    LaneSelection --> STANDARD: risk 3-5, ≤6 files
    LaneSelection --> HIGHRISK: risk 6+, or auth/payment/schema

    DIRECT --> Implement: no plan needed
    FAST --> Plan: inline bullets
    STANDARD --> Plan: PLAN.md required
    HIGHRISK --> Plan: PLAN.md + ADR required

    Implement --> Test
    Test --> Review

    Review --> Pass: tests pass
    Review --> Repair: issues found
    Repair --> Implement: cycle < max_cycles
    Repair --> Stopped: max_cycles reached

    Pass --> ReleaseGate
    Stopped --> [*]: stop condition triggered

    ReleaseGate --> Merged: gate passes
    ReleaseGate --> Blocked: gate fails
    Blocked --> Repair

    Merged --> Score
    Score --> LessonExtraction
    LessonExtraction --> ROIUpdate
    ROIUpdate --> [*]: routing improved
